@startuml
skinparam titleFontSize 24
skinparam titleFontStyle bold
skinparam monochrome true
title Bay Status State Transition

[*] --> Available : Bay initialized

Available --> Reserved : Service order assigned
Available --> OutOfService : Bay closed/damaged

Reserved --> Occupied : Service starts
Reserved --> Available : Reservation cancelled

Occupied --> Cleaning : Service completed
Occupied --> UnderMaintenance : Bay needs repair

Cleaning --> Available : Cleaning done

UnderMaintenance --> Available : Maintenance completed

OutOfService --> UnderMaintenance : Repair scheduled
OutOfService --> Available : Reopened

Available --> [*] : Bay decommissioned

Available : Ready for assignment
Available : No active service

Occupied : Service in progress
Occupied : Employee working
Occupied : Cannot be reassigned

Reserved : Assigned but not started
Reserved : Awaiting service start

@enduml
